Title: The DOLPHIN Speedup-Learning System
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: CERN/3.0 Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 15:55:40 GMT Content-Type: text/html Content-Length: 1750 Last-Modified: Monday, 11-Dec-95 16:42:34 GMT The DOLPHIN Speedup-Learning System DOLPHIN DOLPHIN is a system which combines Inductive Logic Programming (i.e. FOIL) and Explanation-Based Learning (i.e. EBG) to learn search-control rules for eliminating backtracking in Prolog programs.
